		</div>
	</div>
</div>Light combo fields are the ones that remove conditions and can be a lifesaver when facing a necromancer type of mob. Dropping the elixir gun 5 and then firing bolts through it helps continue to cleanse people after fumigate is on CD and keeps things in check.<br />
<br />
Engineers and Elementalists have the most self combo opportunities because of all of the abilities. Engineers just require certain loadouts versus elementalists swapping attunements at the right times.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="after_content">
				
                                       
                                 
				
		        		<blockquote class="signature restore"><div class="signaturecontainer"><a href="http://us.battle.net/wow/en/character/hellscream/Wz/advanced" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://us.battle.net/wow/en/characte...am/Wz/advanced</a></div></blockquote>
				
                                        
			</div>
			
			<div class="cleardiv"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
